Commentary: oooh close! Rubel's got some strength in that shoulder. Bangs this in back of a length outside off, gets it to skid rapidly in and go past Warner's edge

Commentary: back of a length outside off, goes for the pull, is too late on it. Bunts it off the inside edge into the leg side. Rubel too quick for Warner at the moment
